**Spec**: [specs/001-time-tracker/spec.md](../../specs/001-time-tracker/spec.md)  
**Branch**: `001-time-tracker`

### Stack (constitution + ADRs)

- Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript strict
- Zustand + `persist` → `localStorage` key `time-tracker:v1`
- Tailwind v4 + tokens from `DESIGN.md` (Precision Focus)
- Base UI (`@base-ui/react`) wrappers in `src/components/ui/`
- Icons: `@heroicons/react` (outline/solid per wireframe; FR-030)
- Vitest + Testing Library; TDD on `src/features/time-tracker/lib/` and `store/`

### Structure

- Routes: `src/app/(tracker)/` → `/`, `/proyectos`, `/historial`
- Domain: `src/features/time-tracker/` (components, store, lib, testing)
- Wireframes: `specs/001-time-tracker/assets/LB-TT-img-*.png`

### Key commands

